         <sourceDesc>
            <p>This TEI Corpus gathers and encodes correspondence from Sergei Prokofiev during the year 1924. Each letter is transcribed in a separate file.</p>
            <p><persName ref="#Demasy_Paul">Paul Demasy</persName> gives news about the play <title type="work">Judith</title> to <persName ref="#SSP">Prokofiev</persName>, who is beginning to doubt <persName ref="#Rubinstein_Ida">Ida Rubinstein</persName>'s commitment.</p>
            <p>Incipit: J’ai vu cet après-midi une personne qui connait fort bien <persName ref="#Rubinstein_Ida"><abbr>Mme R.</abbr></persName>.</p>
